Not sure what you mean buy accumulator or standard. I am referring to the 
credit unit and keypad combo located at the top/right/ front of the box. The 
wiper arm is the one in the credit unit. Yes about the pin, once the wiper 
arm in the credit unit starts to rotate (after a bump from me) then it makes 
the correct pulses from the converter and all other operations work fine.

